{"tid":1600511,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2個月前我都係諗自治左推獨立，但宜家個勢去緊","createTime":"2019-09-28T15:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T03:14:09.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"002d9cd30ec221ba2439c047d43b18c0f86df865","tid":1600511,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"我講真雙普選，標題個自治係用返巴打講法。97後港人治港自治係一直個講法，係近排中國政府改左講法，我唔打算跟住佢改講法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2個月前，我都係諗真雙普選左，香港人有屬於自己o既政府同議會，叫做守得到下，再諗辦法收返各種權力、推新憲法、唔理中方之類香港獨立。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但之後黑警唔做野，人人知道，你俾人搞、俾人挑機、俾人斬，黑警黑到底，唔只冇影，你搵黑警投訴，分分鐘原告變被告，俾黑警捉返轉頭。最終變成市民自己執行公義、自己處理糾紛。咁我地自己做 Do It Yourself，一樣可以應用o係政府同五大訴求。根本個勢就係咁發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連十一將會出o既宣言都係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3nvLHVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3nvLHVJ.jpg&h=55410de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSolomon Yue 都睇左：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1177586710567219200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1177586710567219200&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=22f223d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1177586710567219200&h=3cd29b38\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1177586710567219200</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲最鐘意大包圍，早排先叫人大膽叫香港革命，呢排又崇禎上吊圖，城邦派都預左呢個趨勢。到時雲粉又可以講老師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6a3e6b59fc92acc853ba2e94ce20bdda2e44ea","tid":1600511,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"去緊 我推緊<br />\n<br />\n入黎投票呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「光 復 香 港」  廢 除 《 聯 合 聲 明 》 第 三 次 公 投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">